Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:36.99,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Imma go and do it my way　邪魔させない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:39.58,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Making my way to the top
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.52,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}堂々としてる I know だって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:43.46,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Proud of my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:45.71,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Manners? I left them behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:49.21,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Hold up hold up 抑えようなんて無駄 Duh duh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:53.47,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Shout out shout out 引き金になる Sound now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:01:55.68,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Boy you’re playing with fire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.31,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}負ける気しないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.39,0:02:02.73,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Don’t stop 志込めた銃弾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:07.82,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}狙い定めて Don’t look back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:09.19,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Oh yeah oh yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.11,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Oh yeah oh yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.11,0:02:11.53,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Giving you my attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:15.55,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}躊躇わないのが Mood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:19.11,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}信じないなら I’ll prove
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.29,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}So I’m giving you my attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:24.46,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:26.33,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}とめられない You can’t kill my vibe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:27.63,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}自由に I can blow your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:29.47,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}何度だって You’ll see me rise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:30.92,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Tryna get to me and pay the price
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:33.97,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}描いた未来へ　進んで行くだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:36.78,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Won’t look back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:42.02,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Giving you my attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:45.15,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}躊躇わないのが Mood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:47.99,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}信じないなら I’ll prove
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:50.73,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}So I’m giving you my attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:53.50,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Attitude
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.28,0:01:36.99,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}走自己的路 莫要阻拦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.99,0:01:39.58,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}迈向巅峰
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.52,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}昂首挺胸 因为我知道
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.52,0:01:43.46,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}为我骄傲的人生
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.46,0:01:45.71,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}别跟我谈规矩
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.00,0:01:49.21,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}让我住手？ 想限制我就是徒劳
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.21,0:01:53.47,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}震耳欲聋 此刻扳机声响起
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.18,0:01:55.68,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}小子 你很张狂
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.31,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}感觉不会输
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.39,0:02:02.73,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}别停 装填决心的子弹
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.73,0:02:07.82,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}瞄准目标 莫回头
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.11,0:02:11.53,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}请看我的态度
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.24,0:02:15.55,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}毫不犹豫的心情
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.27,0:02:19.11,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}若不相信 我将证明
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.29,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}那就请看我的态度
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.46,0:02:26.33,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}不可阻挡 不受干扰气势
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.33,0:02:27.63,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}随手颠覆你的想象
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.63,0:02:29.47,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}周而复始 浴火重生
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.47,0:02:30.92,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}招惹我会付出代价
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.92,0:02:33.97,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}向描绘的未来前行而已
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.97,0:02:36.78,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}莫回头
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.71,0:02:42.02,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}请看我的态度
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.02,0:02:45.15,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}毫不犹豫的心情
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.15,0:02:47.99,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}若不相信 我将证明
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.99,0:02:50.73,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}那就请看我的态度
